{"data":{"page":{"id":"b2b381a5-8784-5f14-8b62-7d77478737bc","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://github.com/gazpachu/andcounting\" target=\"_blank\">Source code</a>\n</p>\n<p>AndCounting is a collabaration with the entrepreneur and designer Cristina Gaston. The idea was to build an Android app to track multiple projects using stop-watches. The prototype was built using the Cordova platform and allowed the user to start/stop projects, rename them and add new ones to the interface. The report button would send an email with the time logged on each project.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1536px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 81.640625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"andcounting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/40e22/andcounting.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/b357d/andcounting.jpg 500w,\n/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/f14cf/andcounting.jpg 1000w,\n/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/40e22/andcounting.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>","fields":{"prefix":"2013"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AndCounting","categories":"android","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/313588cdf323c108dd7d3ca0b6af5711/039c6/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/andcounting/","source":"work"}}